✨ Namma Ooru Thiruvizha – Kovilpatti Event Was a Grand Success! ✨
The incredible ramp walk featuring 10 stunning models from S.M. Sarah Spa, Kovilpatti lit up the stage at Aarthi Mahal! The event was a huge success with vibrant energy, stunning performances, and a supportive crowd. 🌟 A big shoutout to everyone who made it possible and to Murugaveni, International Makeup Artist, for adding her magic touch. 💄👏

🎉 Thank you to all who joined and made it unforgettable! Stay tuned for more exciting events from S.M. Sarah Spa.
